# Trivy ignore file — accepted-risk register for the filesystem misconfig scan.
# Each entry MUST document why the finding is a deliberate design choice, not a defect.

# AVD-KSV-0010 — DaemonSet sets spec.template.spec.hostPID: true
# ACCEPTED (by design): the node DaemonSet (deploy/k8s/daemonset.yaml) needs the
# host PID namespace to enumerate host processes for the "top-N by CPU/RAM"
# host-monitoring collector. This is the core function of the node agent; without
# hostPID it cannot see host processes. The container is otherwise hardened
# (runAsNonRoot, read-only mounts, no host writes). Owner: Pedro Tarrinho.
AVD-KSV-0010
